title: Tinto Basin Outlaws (1941) THE RANGE BUSTERS

sources.title: Tinto Basin Outlaws (1941) THE RANGE BUSTERS
sources.description:
First time on YouTube!
Stars: Ray Corrigan, John 'Dusty' King, Max Terhune
Director: S. Roy Luby

The Range Busters enlist in Teddy Roosevelt's Rough Riders during the Spanish-American War, but are mustered out and sent to Wyoming to clean up a cattle-rustling situation that is affecting the Army's meat supply.
